      "content": "everyone says a professional or a friend will help but they don't get it. they just say \"it'll get better\" like it's some magical thing that just happens. but what if it doesn't? what if this is just how it is now? i look at my life and there is literally nothing left. it's like i'm just a ghost walking around waiting for something to happen. it feels like the only way to actually stop the weight is to just... not be here.",
